race.comment: SEA ADMIRAL (1) resumes for the Thompson yard and is the danger. Won a Kembla Maiden two back fresh and has prepared for this with an easy trial win at Kembla Grange. Will be naturally improved and goes close. LIGHTLY SPARKLED (7) resumes and would be a hope if presented forward this time around. She went close at Kembla Grange this grade two starts back and the market should guide to her readiness. BATTLE WARRIOR (12) is well-bred and spiked his figures winning a Maiden here comfortably. Looked good early doors and looks to have turned the corner. He can stalk the speed from a handy barrier. TANGO ON (8) is not out of this based on his last start win at Orange.
